Ecopetrol SA (ECOPETL) ,  Colombia â€™s largest
oil company, said repair work is under way on an oil pipeline
and a propane duct damaged by mudslides in Guaduas, north of
Bogota.  Ecopetrol and the Energy & Mining Ministry have activated
